{"tid":274173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Iron man 2 伏筆？","createTime":"2017-06-07T06:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T02:56:19.000Z","uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f081a3c053cba45cc56e455b57332668816c948a","tid":274173,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:34:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/V6y33HtbAP0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FV6y33HtbAP0&d=RqhwnB06MJQCJkBLgkiVqrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=68a2d86d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/V6y33HtbAP0</a><br />\n1分09秒，tony啱啱俾人綁架完翻美國，叫司機開車<br />\n個司機係佢保鑣，叫Happy<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LknU0X5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLknU0X5.jpg&h=731645c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但Tony竟然叫佢Logan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重點係！</span></span>睇下佢地坐咩車！<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/24/195905_79fcfb5065fecee9f360f188327a965a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F24%2F195905_79fcfb5065fecee9f360f188327a965a.jpg&h=37e4cd13&s={SIZE}\" />⼁<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tA7wcW7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtA7wcW7.jpg&h=d22591fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Logan!!!!!!</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68jLaHb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68jLaHb.jpg&h=8c46e34e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係同一架但都係豪華房車，好地地做乜無啦啦叫人Logan?<br />\nIron man1係2008年上，Logan係2017年上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實可能係巧合既，不過如果係伏筆就真心屈機"},{"pid":"2b071f25c41d9fd93eaf4fdce795fb3090a8198b","tid":274173,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:35:01.000Z","msg":"漫畫有無講"},{"pid":"2e1aa86ff0fc145bdfc7daa91e5f0737ce750dad","tid":274173,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:39:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>漫畫有無講</blockquote><br />\nTony stark係講Hogan<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係Logan</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c34994e274430aff8455da6386928d6e82acbe64","tid":274173,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:40:41.000Z","msg":"Happy 5個字<br />\nLogan 5個字<br />\n<br />\n5+5=10=<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">iron man two</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又binc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a957f5d351c2d13540e0bfd4cc31c1e5b0978017","tid":274173,"uid":121704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:42:59.000Z","msg":"人地係叫Hogan唔係Logan<br